{"tid":1703531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一直以黎警甴既致命弱點都無人針對","createTime":"2019-11-10T10:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T02:53:14.000Z","uid":287032,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5722eca44cfee65573edb0f5eb645964d6d3dbde","tid":1703531,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:20:54.000Z","msg":"佢地既弱點就係 體力<br />\n再講多次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">體力</span></span><br />\n<br />\n試想像佢地成10幾20kg gear<br />\n仲要不斷跑衝警杯<br />\n可以保證 跑兩小時體力已經消耗左9成<br />\n人地跑42公里馬拉松都跑到就黎死咁<br />\n何況有gear帶豬嘴既popo?<br />\n如果遇到曝曬/大雨天氣體力下滑就更快<br />\n<br />\n其實如果睇返過往紀錄<br />\n例如85三罷<br />\n101開花<br />\n蒙面法開花<br />\n18區悼念開花<br />\n大家可以睇到一到深夜時份警力就會大減<br />\n唔係因為戰術原因 而係佢地真係需要保充體力同休息<br />\n同時指揮高層就會係呢段時間部署黎緊既大圍捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁有咩方法可以針對呢個弱點？<br />\n就係 意志<br />\n再講多次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">意志</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我都知大家夜晚或者通宵開完花會好攰<br />\n如果你覺得攰<br />\n警甴既攰係你既至少雙倍<br />\n如果大家堅持連續三日三夜開花(可以輪更）<br />\n唔比機會佢地休息<br />\n基本上佢地體力就會崩潰<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n大家要小心<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">休息留力陷阱撚</span></span><br />\n每次既休息留力其實係幫警甴回氣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7d2f6fc5c5e14ddf025d9684df5c10666105aa6","tid":1703531,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"我地既優勢就係人數同體力"},{"pid":"18b7c57a9450ef07b61148571cf23c59feea0c21","tid":1703531,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"班廢中邊夠後生體力黎"},{"pid":"28de81c6212d914615de1e6ed90629a59ac3b785","tid":1703531,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"體力"},{"pid":"327e4eaace7c42b11f1dbfe5a1715eba34584484","tid":1703531,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"意志"},{"pid":"bdbdb1cf3f27d61018cf8cc3ff2476a9c6ebcd9a","tid":1703531,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"小心休息撚"},{"pid":"90d88c1de31107ca9fef24e6ba7959131e42a796","tid":1703531,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"唔可以比佢地罰企"},{"pid":"186ebc9e65f0dda2cc5f24495ddf93cd2066c305","tid":1703531,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"要不斷消耗佢地體力"},{"pid":"d5e592076351d6465c8a9d9aaffda2125c3e55ac","tid":1703531,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"成班封站訓覺 vs 遊行左幾個鐘既兄弟。。。"},{"pid":"e0afbc522d381fdc904745e6f4025c1436546967","tid":1703531,"uid":32675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"佢地既弱點係收工,無晒力攰到仆街既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fffb8e0de356819fb040e573eb7e5f365f6de9e","tid":1703531,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0afbc522d381fdc904745e6f4025c1436546967","tid":1703531,"uid":32675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"佢地既弱點係收工,無晒力攰到仆街既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"405c18a3ca8cf6dae0df342238af632a2d23e872","tid":1703531,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:35:19.000Z","msg":"一百萬老解，基本上無限體"},{"pid":"54378e0a28361adbf36101004dbe840a554cd770","tid":1703531,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:35:49.000Z","msg":"佢地有主動權選擇何時何地出擊, 後面仲有車開住冷氣支援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4be708725d7cb8b8b87f65982526ac74c587b91","tid":1703531,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited